body:
GoT crackships:

  • Daenerys & Jaime: Daenerys would see him as a good man, as someone who did mistakes but decided to fight for the good. Despite their age difference, they could be a power couple.
  • Robb & Margaery: Margaery is the kind, gentle, powerful woman Robb wants and needs. Talisa was really similar to her, just a bit more naïve and less smart (no offence to her, I loved her). If Robb was a bit smarter too, Margaery would be perfect for him.
  • (Young) Bran & Myrcella: they would have been a cute couple. Bran, after all, was a good child before becoming the Three-Eyed Raven. Myrcella with him could have been less “damsel-in-distress” and Bran would have protected her.
  • Robb & Missandei: Missandei is really similar to Talisa, so I think that they could have worked in a different scenario.
  • Loras & Theon: I can picture them very well together. Both are brave, yet a bit hesitant, so together they would be a good match. Not sure why, I’ve always thought of Theon as someone who was more into boys.

Please don’t attack me! I love the main couples as well but I like thinking of other craskships :)
